{"type":null,"faqId":18974,"title":"荣耀畅玩4X天气时钟时间和系统时间显示不一致？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>如果是天气时钟widget时间显示与系统时间显示不统一，请您先确认下手机设置的是哪个时区。具体步骤：查看设置-》日期和时间-》选择市区，确认所选择的时区与天气时钟widget显示城市的时区是否一致。如果不一致，该现象为正常现象。原因：系统时间显示是根据手机设置的时区显示的，而天气时钟widget的时间显示则是根据widget设置的城市的时区确定，所以系统时间和天气时钟widget显示的时间可能会出现不一致的现象。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":11,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2037","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422325563000,"seriesProductName":"Cherry-CL10,Cherry-CL20,CherryPlus-TL00,CherryPlus-TL00H,CherryPlus-TL00M,CherryPlus-TL10,CherryPlus-UL00,CherryPlus-UL10","visitedTimes":533,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀畅玩4X,天气时钟,系统时间,显示不一致","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}